{
  "stem": "20021.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had to somehow get papers which would hide the fact that we were in Russia.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because as such, you know, the Germans-- every once in a while, the Germans would pick up somebody and shoot them for whatever infraction of the rules were.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They terrorized the town that way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If there was any infraction, you'd be shot on the spot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember one day a girl which she went to the same school that I went, although we were not in the same class, she was just shot one day.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She was taken out of the cemetery and the gestapo shot her for whatever reason.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the rules-- the laws were such that you practically didn't have any rights.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And yet, most Jews were still surviving and believing and really, at that point it looked like they had a good chance to survive.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we arrived back in Tarnow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First we hid for two months until the papers were arranged and so forth.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the fact that we were in Russia was concealed in those papers, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In other words, the papers were so arranged as though they were issued right then when everybody else's papers were issued.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my-- my mother persuaded this Edwin Hauser, was now the owner of my father's factory, to give us jobs.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we had jobs and we worked.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How did you get back?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Physically how did you get back?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well it so happens, we paid a big bribe to a German who put us in his private car and transported us out from Lwow to-- and my mother knew somebody and arranged with somebody.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was simply doing it for the money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we arrived and we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
